name: $busy
desc: Indicates that the time interval is free for scheduling.

name: $free
desc: Indicates that the time interval is busy and that the interval cannot be scheduled.

name: $busy-unavailable
desc: Indicates that the time interval is busy because one or more events have been tentatively scheduled for that interval.

name: $busy-tentative
desc: This instance should not have been part of this patient's medical record.
